text: Bash-Ilchikeyevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Meshchegarovsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 337 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 43 km from Maloyaz, 9 km from Mursalimkino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Bash-Ilchikeyevo
